

This archive contains the distribution Acpi-Battery,
version 0.001:

  Inspired in Acpi::Battery, this module gets the contents of the directory '/sys/class' in terms of 'classes' (ArrayRef of directories in /sys/class), 'devices' (ArrayRef of subdirectory in class) and 'attributes' (HashRef attributes => values, from the contents of devices directory).

